---

<Header />

<main class="about">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>About <span class="brand">AmicBridge</span></h1>
      <p>
        AmicBridge connects people who have something to give with those who
        truly need it. We‚Äôre not a bank or a middleman chasing profit ‚Äî we‚Äôre
        the bridge between generosity and opportunity.
      </p>
    </div>
    <img
      src="/bridge.jpg"
      alt="AmicBridge concept - people connected by trust"
      class="hero-img"
    />
  </section>

  <section class="mission">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      In every community, someone is searching for a way forward ‚Äî a loan, a
      tool, or a helping hand ‚Äî and someone else has the means to offer it.
      AmicBridge makes that connection safe, fair, and simple. We use clear
      agreements, encrypted systems, and human-centered design to make modern
      finance feel personal again.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="values">
    <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
    <div class="value-grid">
      {values.map((value) => (
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="icon">{value.icon}</div>
          <h3>{value.title}</h3>
          <p>{value.description}</p>
        </div>
